<START:organization> Spare5 <END> turns them into something else – call them nanoentrepreneurs .
It is n’t a substitute for a job .
It’s a substitute for playing <START:organization> Candy Crush <END> and liking pictures of your friends ’ schnauzer on <START:organization> Facebook <END> .
Rather than spending a dollar to receive fake gold coins in a game , you can use the app to earn actual coins .
