<START:person> Arun Sundararajan <END> , a professor at <START:organization> New York University’s <END> <START:organization> Stern School of Business <END> , says that services like <START:organization> Spare5 <END> can be empowering to people who want more control over when and how they work , even if it ’s for peanuts .
