That’s not to say that some consumers have n’t run into problems .
<START:person> Katherine Kostreva <END> , a marketing and public relations consultant in <START:location> New York <END> , said she had encountered problems with mobile check deposits at <START:organization> Bank of America <END> this year — first for $ 1,400 and then for $ 1,200 .
