Here are some questions about mobile check deposit :
■ How should I sign my check when using mobile deposit ?
Check with your bank for its specific requirements .
In general , adding the phrase “for mobile deposit only ” is a good idea , said <START:person> James DeBello <END> , chief of <START:organization> Mitek <END> , which provides the systems that process mobile check deposits at many banks .
